item.title: S4 E19 - The Offside Rule Needs Simplifying
item.description:
If you had the power to change 1 rule, what would it be? Will says handball rules, Ben says offside rules as it needs simplifying, how? Listen and find out as he explains just as well as Will pronounces team names outside the Premier League.

The usual round up again this week, the Brazilian League is hotting up with 1 game to go, 3 teams still in the hunt for the title. Serie A, La Liga, Bundesliga & Saudi Pro League results and updates packed into another brilliant episode... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/639c8ce16bb5ca00104d60b5
